Fecha modificación: 2022-07-01 Modificado por: Factor IT, Oscar de Dios Cambio: EPIC - 5151 Objetivo del cambio: Se crea la tarea 03_ACTUALIZAR_CUOTA3, para actualizar las columnas DES_CONSU_ADI_DATOS, COD_PERIODO_TIEMPO
Fecha modificación: 2019-12-17 Modificado por: Procalidad, Edwar Pastás Morales Cambio: EPIC - 02134 Objetivo del cambio: Se modifican las tareas 04_AGRUPAR_PLANES y 06_ACTUALIZAR_DETALLES_PLAN, para agregar a la tabla TBL_TMP_CLIEN_DET_PLAN_FIN los campos MIN_INC_LDI_1, MIN_INC_LDI_2 , MIN_INC_LDI_RM y VALOR_ADIC_KB.
Fecha creación: 2019-07-07 Creado por: Procalidad S.A., Joan Vasquez ID 460 Objetivo del nodo: Procedimiento que actualiza la foto de planes a partir de la información cargada en la segunda extracción.

CREATE TEMPORARY TABLE TBL_TMP_CLIEN_DET_PLAN_FIN AS (SELECT DISTINCT A.TMCODE, A.SPCODE, A.TIPO_BOLSA, A.TIPO_CONTROL_MAGUARE, A.TIPO_PLAN, CASE WHEN A.TIPO_MEDIDA = 'Seg' THEN 'SEGUNDOS' WHEN A.TIPO_MEDIDA = 'Min' THEN 'MINUTOS' WHEN A.TIPO_MEDIDA = 'Net' THEN 'NET' WHEN A.TIPO_MEDIDA = 'SMS' THEN 'SMS' ELSE A.TIPO_PLAN END AS TIPO_FACTURACION, A.PLAN_DESC_COMPLETA, A.VLR_CFM_VOZ, A.VLR_CFM_DATOS, A.VLR_CFM_DATOS_IMP, A.MIN_INC_C_F_O, A.MIN_INC_C, A.MIN_INC_F, A.MIN_INC_O, A.CANT_MIN_INC_ELEG_TD, A.CANT_SMS_CLARO_INC, A.CANT_MB_INC_PLAN, A.CANT_MB_BB_INC_PLAN, A.SEGMENTO_PLAN, A.NAVEGACION_PLAN, A.VLR_MIN_INC_CLARO, A.VLR_MIN_INC_FIJOS, A.VLR_MIN_INC_OTROS, A.VLR_MIN_ADIC_CLARO, A.VLR_MIN_ADIC_FIJOS, A.VLR_MIN_ADIC_OTROS, A.VLR_SMS_ADIC_CLARO, A.CANT_ELEG_FIJO, A.CANT_ELEG_ONNET, A.CANT_ELEG_OFFNET, A.CANT_ELEG_TD, A.NOMBRE_CUOTA_PCRF, A.TIPO_NAVEGACION_PCRF, A.TIPO_PLAN_PCRF, A.ROUTING_CATEGORY_BCSC, A.TECNOLOGIA, A.FAMILIA_PLAN, A.CLASE_PLAN, A.MIN_INC_LDI_1, A.MIN_INC_LDI_2, A.MIN_INC_LDI_RM, A.VALOR_ADIC_KB, A.COD_PASE FROM db_dwh_stage.clientes.TBL_TMP_CLIEN_DETALLE_PLAN A INNER JOIN db_dwh_stage.clientes.TBL_TMP_CLIEN_DET_PLAN B ON (A.TMCODE = B.TMCODE AND A.SPCODE = B.SPCODE AND A.VERSION = B.VER)) DISTRIBUTE ON (TMCODE)

UPDATE <%=odiRef.getObjectName("TBL_CLIEN_PLANES")%> A SET TIPO_OFERTA = B.TIPO_OFERTA, BAN_CONVERTIBLE_LDI = B.BAN_CONVERTIBLE_LDI, PSB_MINU_CONV_LDI = B.PSB_MINU_CONV_LDI, PSB_VALOR_CONV_LDI = B.PSB_VALOR_CONV_LDI, PSB_VALOR_CONV_PREFERE_LDI = B.PSB_VALOR_CONV_PREFERE_LDI, PSB_MINU_CONV_ZONA_LDI = B.PSB_MINU_CONV_ZONA_LDI, PSB_VALOR_CONV_ZONA_LDI = B.PSB_VALOR_CONV_ZONA_LDI, PSB_MINU_CONV_PREFERE_LDI = B.PSB_MINU_CONV_PREFERE_LDI FROM ( SELECT TMCODE, SPCODE, MAX(VALOR_KB) AS VALOR_KB, CUOTA, UNIDAD_CUOTA, TIPO_OFERTA, BAN_CONVERTIBLE_LDI, PSB_MINU_CONV_LDI, PSB_VALOR_CONV_LDI, PSB_VALOR_CONV_PREFERE_LDI, PSB_MINU_CONV_ZONA_LDI, PSB_VALOR_CONV_ZONA_LDI, PSB_MINU_CONV_PREFERE_LDI FROM <%=odiRef.getObjectName("TBL_TMP_CLIEN_UPD_PLANES")%> GROUP BY TMCODE, SPCODE, CUOTA, UNIDAD_CUOTA, TIPO_OFERTA, BAN_CONVERTIBLE_LDI, PSB_MINU_CONV_LDI, PSB_VALOR_CONV_LDI, PSB_VALOR_CONV_PREFERE_LDI, PSB_MINU_CONV_ZONA_LDI, PSB_VALOR_CONV_ZONA_LDI, PSB_MINU_CONV_PREFERE_LDI ) B WHERE A.TMCODE = B.TMCODE AND A.SPCODE = B.SPCODE

UPDATE <%=odiRef.getObjectName("TBL_CLIEN_PLANES")%> T1 SET TIPO_BOLSA = NVL(S.TIPO_BOLSA,'NA'), PLAN_DESC_COMPLETA = NVL(S.PLAN_DESC_COMPLETA,'NA'), CLASE_PLAN = NVL(S.CLASE_PLAN,'NA'), VLR_CFM_VOZ = NVL(S.VLR_CFM_VOZ,0), VLR_CFM_DATOS = NVL(S.VLR_CFM_DATOS,0), VLR_CFM_DATOS_IMP = NVL(S.VLR_CFM_DATOS_IMP,0), MIN_INC_C_F_O = NVL(S.MIN_INC_C_F_O,0), MIN_INC_C = NVL(S.MIN_INC_C,0), MIN_INC_F = NVL(S.MIN_INC_F,0), MIN_INC_O = NVL(S.MIN_INC_O,0), CANT_MIN_INC_ELEG_TD = NVL(S.CANT_MIN_INC_ELEG_TD,0), CANT_SMS_CLARO_INC = NVL(S.CANT_SMS_CLARO_INC,0), CANT_MB_INC_PLAN = NVL(S.CANT_MB_INC_PLAN,0), CANT_MB_BB_INC_PLAN = NVL(S.CANT_MB_BB_INC_PLAN,0), SEGMENTO_PLAN = NVL(S.SEGMENTO_PLAN,'NA'), NAVEGACION_PLAN = NVL(S.NAVEGACION_PLAN,'NA'), VLR_MIN_INC_CLARO = NVL(S.VLR_MIN_INC_CLARO,0), VLR_MIN_INC_FIJOS = NVL(S.VLR_MIN_INC_FIJOS,0), VLR_MIN_INC_OTROS = NVL(S.VLR_MIN_INC_OTROS,0), VAL_MIN_ADIC_CLARO = NVL(S.VLR_MIN_ADIC_CLARO,0), VAL_MIN_ADIC_FIJOS = NVL(S.VLR_MIN_ADIC_FIJOS,0), VAL_MIN_ADIC_OTROS = NVL(S.VLR_MIN_ADIC_OTROS,0), VAL_SMS_ADIC_CLARO = NVL(S.VLR_SMS_ADIC_CLARO,0), VAL_CANT_ELEG_FIJOS = NVL(S.CANT_ELEG_FIJO,0), VAL_CANT_ELEG_ONNET = NVL(S.CANT_ELEG_ONNET,0), VAL_CANT_ELEG_OFFNET = NVL(S.CANT_ELEG_OFFNET,0), CANT_ELEG_TD = NVL(S.CANT_ELEG_TD,0), NOMBRE_CUOTA_PCRF = NVL(S.NOMBRE_CUOTA_PCRF,'NA'), TIPO_NAVEGACION_PCRF = NVL(S.TIPO_NAVEGACION_PCRF,'NA'), TIPO_PLAN_PCRF = NVL(S.TIPO_PLAN_PCRF,'NA'), ROUTING_CATEGORY_BCSC = NVL(S.ROUTING_CATEGORY_BCSC,0), VAL_IVA_SERV_VOZ = NVL(ROUND(S.VAL_IVA_SERV_VOZ,2),0), VAL_IVA_SERV_DATOS = NVL(ROUND(S.VAL_IVA_SERV_DATOS,2),0), VAL_IVA_SERV_DATOS_IMP = NVL(ROUND(S.VAL_IVA_SERV_DATOS_IMP,2),0), VAL_IVA_SMS = NVL(ROUND(S.VAL_IVA_SMS,2),0), CANT_MIN_INC_LDI_1 = NVL(S.MIN_INC_LDI_1,0), CANT_MIN_INC_LDI_2 = NVL(S.MIN_INC_LDI_2,0), CANT_MIN_INC_LDI_RM = NVL(S.MIN_INC_LDI_RM,0), VAL_ADIC_KB = NVL(S.VALOR_ADIC_KB,0), COD_PASE = NVL(S.COD_PASE,'NA') FROM ( SELECT DISTINCT B.TMCODE, B.SPCODE, B.TIPO_BOLSA, B.PLAN_DESC_COMPLETA, B.CLASE_PLAN, B.VLR_CFM_VOZ, B.VLR_CFM_DATOS, B.VLR_CFM_DATOS_IMP, B.MIN_INC_C_F_O, B.MIN_INC_C, B.MIN_INC_F, B.MIN_INC_O, B.CANT_MIN_INC_ELEG_TD, B.CANT_SMS_CLARO_INC, B.CANT_MB_INC_PLAN, B.CANT_MB_BB_INC_PLAN, B.SEGMENTO_PLAN, B.NAVEGACION_PLAN, B.VLR_MIN_INC_CLARO, B.VLR_MIN_INC_FIJOS, B.VLR_MIN_INC_OTROS, B.VLR_MIN_ADIC_CLARO, B.VLR_MIN_ADIC_FIJOS, B.VLR_MIN_ADIC_OTROS, B.VLR_SMS_ADIC_CLARO, B.CANT_ELEG_FIJO, B.CANT_ELEG_ONNET, B.CANT_ELEG_OFFNET, B.CANT_ELEG_TD, B.NOMBRE_CUOTA_PCRF, B.TIPO_NAVEGACION_PCRF, B.TIPO_PLAN_PCRF, B.ROUTING_CATEGORY_BCSC, B.MIN_INC_LDI_1, B.MIN_INC_LDI_2, B.MIN_INC_LDI_RM, B.VALOR_ADIC_KB, B.COD_PASE, C.VAL_IVA_SERV_VOZ, C.VAL_IVA_SERV_DATOS, C.VAL_IVA_SERV_DATOS_IMP, C.VAL_IVA_SMS FROM <%=odiRef.getObjectName("TBL_CLIEN_PLANES")%> A INNER JOIN TBL_TMP_CLIEN_DET_PLAN_FIN B ON (A.COD_PLAN = NVL(B.TMCODE,'-1')||'-'||NVL(B.SPCODE,'-1')) LEFT JOIN TBL_TMP_CLIEN_MPULKTMB_FULL_AUX C ON (A.COD_PLAN = C.COD_PLAN) ) S WHERE T1.COD_PLAN = NVL(S.TMCODE,'-1')||'-'||NVL(S.SPCODE,'-1')

CREATE TEMPORARY TABLE TBL_TMP_CLIEN_MPULKTMB_FULL_AUX AS (SELECT COD_PLAN, SUM(VAL_IVA_SERV_VOZ) VAL_IVA_SERV_VOZ, SUM(VAL_IVA_SERV_DATOS) VAL_IVA_SERV_DATOS, SUM(VAL_IVA_SERV_DATOS_IMP) VAL_IVA_SERV_DATOS_IMP, SUM(VAL_IVA_SMS) VAL_IVA_SMS FROM (SELECT NVL(TMCODE,'-1')||'-'||NVL(SPCODE,'-1') COD_PLAN, CASE WHEN SNCODE = 3013 THEN TAXRATE ELSE 0 END VAL_IVA_SERV_VOZ, CASE WHEN SNCODE = 11538 THEN TAXRATE ELSE 0 END VAL_IVA_SERV_DATOS, CASE WHEN SNCODE = 11537 THEN TAXRATE ELSE 0 END VAL_IVA_SERV_DATOS_IMP, CASE WHEN SNCODE = 3004 THEN TAXRATE ELSE 0 END VAL_IVA_SMS FROM <%=odiRef.getInfo("SRC_CATALOG")%>.<%=odiRef.getInfo("SRC_SCHEMA")%>.INH_EXT_MPULKTMB_FULL_AUX) A GROUP BY COD_PLAN) --FROM INH_EXT_MPULKTMB_FULL_AUX) A GROUP BY COD_PLAN) DISTRIBUTE ON (COD_PLAN)

UPDATE <%=odiRef.getObjectName("TBL_CLIEN_PLANES")%> T1 SET TIPO_CONTROL_MAGUARE = NVL(S.TIPO_CONTROL_MAGUARE,'Sin Tipo Control'), TIPO_PLAN = NVL(S.TIPO_PLAN,'Sin Tipo'), TIPO_FACTURACION = NVL(S.TIPO_FACTURACION,'Sin Tipo') FROM ( SELECT DISTINCT B.TIPO_CONTROL_MAGUARE, B.TIPO_PLAN, B.TIPO_FACTURACION, B.TMCODE, B.SPCODE FROM <%=odiRef.getObjectName("TBL_CLIEN_PLANES")%> A INNER JOIN TBL_TMP_CLIEN_DET_PLAN_FIN B ON (A.TMCODE = NVL(B.TMCODE,'-1') AND A.SPCODE = NVL(B.SPCODE,'-1')) ) S WHERE PRODUCTO = 'Postpago' AND T1.TMCODE = NVL(S.TMCODE,'-1') AND T1.SPCODE = NVL(S.SPCODE,'-1')

UPDATE <%=odiRef.getObjectName("TBL_CLIEN_PLANES")%> A SET DES_CONSU_ADI_DATOS = B.DES_CONSU_ADI_DATOS, COD_PERIODO_TIEMPO = B.COD_PERIODO_TIEMPO FROM ( SELECT TMCODE,DES_CONSU_ADI_DATOS, COD_PERIODO_TIEMPO FROM <%=odiRef.getObjectName("TBL_TMP_CLIEN_UPD_PLANES")%> GROUP BY TMCODE, DES_CONSU_ADI_DATOS, COD_PERIODO_TIEMPO ) B WHERE A.TMCODE = B.TMCODE
